content:
TopLevelNameCollisionOptions Enum

Definition

Specifies additional information about a forest trust collision when the stem.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType* property value is ForestTrustCollisionType.

In this Article

[System.Flags]
public enum TopLevelNameCollisionOptions
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
Enum
TopLevelNameCollisionOptions

Examples

CollisionType ForestTrustCollisionType

Fields

DisabledByAdmin

The forest trust account was disabled by administrative action.
DisabledByConflict

The forest trust account was disabled due to a conflict with an existing forest trust account.
NewlyCreated

The forest trust account has been created and is disabled.
None

No action has occurred.
